{"tid":388066,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[iOS/Android] 廢青整手機Game系列！之第一隻","createTime":"2017-09-05T07:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T14:17:20.000Z","uid":15584,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70cb5782a8b2b402ab59bd0605a88d418acd240e","tid":388066,"uid":15584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:21:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我地幾丁友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最近整左一隻手機遊戲，比各位巴打搭下車玩，返工放工消磨下時間。事不宜遲，我地講下隻遊戲：「Bludy」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/05/151428_f64f9460f57262330cf44281f658559b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F05%2F151428_f64f9460f57262330cf44281f658559b.png&h=80e7651d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/05/151441_3d11a25deed10c6c18ddaedb08994b36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F05%2F151441_3d11a25deed10c6c18ddaedb08994b36.jpg&h=8837e691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻係我地第一隻遊戲，主題係一個藍色嘅太空人想上太空。我地幫佢改左個名叫Bludy，其實係Blue Buddy既簡寫(唔係bloody)。詳情係點，就賣個關子，留比各位巴打下載黎睇下(睇圖其實大概都估到)。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nApple Apps Store: <br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/bludy/id1278212243?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fbludy%2Fid1278212243%3Fmt%3D8&d=ExK9dujywAhJx97VqR7CPoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=270f6915\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/bludy/id1278212243?mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle Play Store: <br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/sMHMj8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsMHMj8&d=ExK9dujywAhJx97VqR7CPoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=32d21903\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/sMHMj8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/05/151523_c73db30ad427cc0e80480be01b8d7492.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F05%2F151523_c73db30ad427cc0e80480be01b8d7492.png&h=8e2f908d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我地冇咩錢可以用黎宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以希望各位巴打支持我地啲本土小型創作，而我地都好想藉著手機遊戲，比巴打們輕鬆一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。我地目標係每一個月就會出一隻新嘅小品遊戲，或者係現有嘅遊戲加入新嘅玩法同更新。<br />\n<br />\n如果巴打想支持下我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，可以like我地嘅Facebook，或者follow我地嘅instagram，我地會定時更新，第一時間可以知道我地整左咩遊戲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFacebook Page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ahha.HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fahha.HK%2F&d=ExK9dujywAhJx97VqR7CPoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=7cd9f30e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ahha.HK/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ahha_hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fahha_hk%2F&d=ExK9dujywAhJx97VqR7CPoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=10c59686\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/ahha_hk/</a><br />\nWebsite: <a href=\"https://ahhahk.wixsite.com/ahhahk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fahhahk.wixsite.com%2Fahhahk&d=ExK9dujywAhJx97VqR7CPoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=ad25d9f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://ahhahk.wixsite.com/ahhahk</a>"},{"pid":"ce1938a7b1ad0c750e4044fa5bdb13cfc6e42d5c","tid":388066,"uid":15584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11494ac560f52f3e738424ffc355da6c7e435f38","tid":388066,"uid":15584,"like":0,"dislike":